cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper deals with algorithmic fairness in a sequential learning setting, specifically in the context of multi-armed bandits. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Cryptography and Security). The paper also touches upon the concept of feedback loops, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
